text: Waltersdorf may refer to: In Austria: * Bad Waltersdorf, in the Hartberg district, Styria * Waltersdorf an der March, a part of Drösing, Lower Austria * Waltersdorf, part of Judenburg, Styria * Waltersdorf, part of Neukirchen an der Vöckla, Upper Austria * Waltersdorf, part of Staatz, Lower Austria In Germany: * Waltersdorf, Thuringia, in the Saale-Holzland district, Thuringia * Waltersdorf, Heideblick, a part of Heideblick in the Dahme-Spreewald district, Brandenburg * Waltersdorf, Schönefeld, a part of Schönefeld in the Dahme- Spreewald district, Brandenburg * Waltersdorf, Löbau-Zittau, a part of Großschönau in the Löbau-Zittau district, Saxony * Waltersdorf, Sächsische Schweiz, a part of Porschdorf in the Sächsische Schweiz district, Saxony In the Czech Republic: * An older name of Vrchy In Poland: * An older name of Mniszków * An older name of Nielestno * An older name of Niegosławice, Lubusz Voivodeship in the Silesian Voivodeship In Romania: * Waltersdorf, the German name for Dumitrița Commune, Bistriţa-Năsăud County
